data.text:
To listen to a live stream of WTMD’s regular broadcast, click on the first button.

Baltimore music abounds on WTMD’s HD2 Channel, click on the second button. Hear back-to-back hours of your favorite Baltimore bands plus encore presentations of the weekend, specialty programs you may have missed.

Now you’ll have a second chance to hear Brooks Long and 6 Degrees of Soul, Detour with Paul Hartman, and Afternoons on TMD.
